body:
Jön Marvel Ultimate Alliance 3 Nintendo Switch-re

A játékot a Team Ninja fejleszti (Ninja Gaiden, Dead or Alive) és várhatóan jövőre fog megjelenni, de pontosabb dátumot nem tettek közzé.

blog.description: Spoiler warning for GoT and Endgame. Proceed with caution.

summary:
First of all: I am so HYPED about the movie already.
Second: I feel like the trailer was the perfect representation of the MCU....
body:
First of all: I am so HYPED about the movie already.

Second: I feel like the trailer was the perfect representation of the MCU. Drama (monologue, music), lots of Emotion (Steve cries, Tony dies) and the right amount of humor (Scott). If the film is going to be the same, I’ll love it.

Third: Goddamnit, someone rescue Tony and Nebula already!

summary: Avengers: Endgame trailer is out, watch it here
title: Avengers: Endgame trailer is out, watch it here
body:
A most awaited trailer of Avengers 4 which is titled Avengers: Endgame has been released. Fans have been waiting tightly for the trailer as they watched last part and saw Thanos wiping out half of the world.



The trailer guarantees a story beginning from a point where the last part finished. Our superheroes Iron Man, Captain America, Hulk, Black Widow, and Thor are trying to analyse the destruction.



The trailer additionally shapes people for a passionate ending of the universe.



Curiously, last part has been most liked Hollywood movies throughout the world. It performed a huge business all over the globe, particularly in India.
